disposeAbstractGraphicsDeviceActionOnEDT

Runnable disposeAbstractGraphicsDeviceActionOnEDT
Disposes the AbstractGraphicsDevice within EDT, since resources created (X11: Display), must be destroyed in the same thread, where they have been created.
